{"id": "art-74", "label": "Art. 74", "title": "Art. 74", "slug": "art-74", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 74 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1449095684\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2410\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1449095684\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În orice factur&#259;, ofert&#259;, comand&#259;, tarif,\nprospect <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> alte documente <span class=SpellE>întrebuin&#355;ate</span>\nîn <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;</span>, emanând de la o societate, trebuie\ns&#259; se <span class=SpellE>men&#355;ioneze</span> denumirea, forma\njuridic&#259;, sediul social, num&#259;rul din registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> codul unic de înregistrare. Sunt exceptate\nbonurile fiscale emise de aparatele de marcat electronice, care vor cuprinde\nelementele prev&#259;zute de <span class=SpellE>legisla&#355;ia</span> din\ndomeniu.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1656842424\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2409\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1656842424\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dac&#259; societatea pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\nopteaz&#259; pentru un sistem dualist de administrare, în conformitate cu\nprevederile art. 153, documentele prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) vor <span\nclass=SpellE>con&#355;ine</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>men&#355;iunea</span> &quot;societate administrat&#259; în sistem\ndualist&quot;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_525735907\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2408\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_525735907\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În documentele prev&#259;zute la alin. (1), dac&#259;\nacestea provin de la o societate cu r&#259;spundere limitat&#259;, se va <span\nclass=SpellE>men&#355;iona</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> capitalul\nsocial, iar dac&#259; ele provin de la o societate pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\nsau în comandit&#259; pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, se vor <span\nclass=SpellE>men&#355;iona</span> atât capitalul social subscris, cât <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cel v&#259;rsat.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_477882869\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2407\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_477882869\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)În <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span> în care\ndocumentele prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) sunt emise de o sucursal&#259;, acestea\ntrebuie s&#259; <span class=SpellE>men&#355;ioneze</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\noficiul registrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> la care a fost\nînregistrat&#259; sucursala <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> num&#259;rul ei\nde înregistrare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1350852977\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2406\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1350852977\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Dac&#259; societatea <span class=SpellE>de&#355;ine</span>\no pagin&#259; de internet proprie, <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;iile</span>\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (1) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> (3) vor fi\npublicate <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pe pagina de internet a <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>CAPITOLUL <span class=SpellE>II:Societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nîn nume colectiv</span></b></p>"}